**Summary of ASX Announcement (Appendix 3C - Buy-back Notification):**  

- **Type:** On-market buy-back (ongoing)  
- **Securities bought back (previous day):** 25,500 RF1 units  
- **Cumulative buy-back to date:** 20,871,719 RF1 units (11.1% of total issued)  
- **Daily consideration paid:** AUD 72,757 (avg. price ~AUD 2.85/unit)  
- **Price range (previous day):** AUD 2.82–2.86/unit  
- **Buy-back window:** 25/7/2024 to 24/7/2025 (10/12 limit compliance)  
- **Broker:** Shaw & Partners  

*No material deviations or new capital structure impacts identified.*
